                                    </div>Site Actions</h3>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Alert</strong> <br /> custom text javascript pop up message </li>
				<li><strong>Autofill</strong> <br /> autopopulate a form field (using ID) with custom text</li>
				<li><strong>Autofill & Submit</strong> <br /> autopopulate a form field (using ID) and submit form</li>
				<li><strong>Custom site banner</strong> <br /> overlay site banner with custom HTML inside the following output:<br />
				<p class="code">&lt;div class=sitefoil-banner style=z-index:99999;position:fixed;top:0px;width:100%;margin:0px;padding:0px;&gt;Your HTML goes here&lt;/div&gt;</p>

				</li>
				<li><strong>Custom site footer</strong> <br /> overlay site footer with custom HTML inside the following output:<br />
				<p class="code">
					&lt;div class=sitefoil-footer style=z-index:99999;position:fixed;bottom:0px;width:100%;margin:0px;padding:0px;&gt;Your HTML goes here&lt;/div&gt;
				</p>

				</li>
