                                        <span class="glyphicon fa fa-envelope big-glyphicon text-center" style="margin:auto;"></span>
                                    </div>Email Actions</h3>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Send email</strong> <br /> send an email with custom HTML to any recipient email address</li>

			</ul>
		</li>
	</ul>

